    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>重檐 </strong></i>是一款拥有超高自由度的治愈系古风造景游戏。你可以在关卡模式中轻松复现各种唯美的名画，古建，诗词场景，并解锁相关的独特图块；也可以在创造模式中完全自由的摆放各种已解锁的资源，构建属于自己的独特古风世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>关卡模式 - </i></strong>中华文化的电子博物展廊</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重檐把各种名画，历史建筑，诗词等等做成相应的关卡场景，通过三维线稿的形式展现。玩家通过逐一拖拽图块到对应的位置来完成场景的复现。成功放置图块会触发各自独特的互动特效，让您在轻松解压的氛围中完成关卡并解锁大量有趣的独特图块。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>三维线稿场景 - 文化记忆的轮廓</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/aee9251cc81829c85a91023633efe209.poster.avif?t=1771560476\" width=1080 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/aee9251cc81829c85a91023633efe209.webm?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/aee9251cc81829c85a91023633efe209.mp4?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>独特图块资源 - 寓教于乐的历史博物馆</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/1b149f0b9d68e8e7f0906efb83c2a1c8.webp?t=1771560476\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/1b149f0b9d68e8e7f0906efb83c2a1c8.poster.avif?t=1771560476\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1080 height=564 /></picture></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>拖拽吸附放置 - 轻松解压的复现玩法</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/52644a984ed87f2263cf3e05b1388a93.poster.avif?t=1771560476\" width=1080 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/52644a984ed87f2263cf3e05b1388a93.webm?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/52644a984ed87f2263cf3e05b1388a93.mp4?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>图块放置特效 - 生动治愈的文化互动</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/c23f0314a4a831293a293fb807b67e3f.poster.avif?t=1771560476\" width=1080 height=562 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/c23f0314a4a831293a293fb807b67e3f.webm?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/c23f0314a4a831293a293fb807b67e3f.mp4?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>复现场景 - 解锁独特图块资源</strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/858fa11103a73de0ccc315bc3a984cd5.poster.avif?t=1771560476\" width=1170 height=644 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/858fa11103a73de0ccc315bc3a984cd5.webm?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/858fa11103a73de0ccc315bc3a984cd5.mp4?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>创造模式</strong></i> - 完全自由的古风绘卷</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在创造模式中，你可以完全自由的摆放海量的图块，随心所欲的构建属于自己的古风世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/bafd757880bfdd57500131a438288dfa.poster.avif?t=1771560476\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/bafd757880bfdd57500131a438288dfa.webm?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897300/extras/bafd757880bfdd57500131a438288dfa.mp4?t=1771560476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>丰富的图块种类</i></strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>自由的图块控件</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>参数化的特殊组件</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>定格风格的动画组件</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>无限的绘卷空间</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>【TODO】可互动的特殊模块</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >未来还会给各种特殊模块开发大量可互动的玩法，让重檐这个古风世界更加鲜活起来！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>欢迎关注！</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感兴趣的小伙伴可以添加愿望单！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也欢迎关注我的B站和小红书账号 - <strong>卡卡波比Studio</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我会持续更新游戏的进度~ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q群 730973505</p>",
